const aboutUs = 'We are delighted to have you visit us. Whether you\'re a seeker in search of truth, a new member of the community looking for a home church, we invite you to be our guest at RCCG Peculiar People Assembly. Here, we seek to embody the love and grace of God and to live by His word. This means open arms and an open Bible. Our Church is a clinic for sinners, a home for spiritual maturity, and an outpost for touching the world.';

const mission = 'As received by the General Overseer (G.O.), Pastor E. A. Adeboye, and communicated to the Headquarters leaders, our vision and mission statement shall remain intact, with a qualifying addendum in view of the peculiarity of the demography in the North American region. They are as follows:\n\n1. To make heaven.\n\n2. To take as many people with us.\n\n3. To have a member of RCCG in every family of all nations.\n\n4. To accomplish No. 1 above, holiness will be our lifestyle.\n\n5. To accomplish No. 2 and 3 above, we will plant churches within five minutes walking distance in every city and town of developing countries and within ten minutes driving distance in every city and town of developed countries.\n\n6. We will pursue these objectives until every Nation in the world is reached for the Lord Jesus Christ.';

